{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"I18N","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/I18N","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>i18n（取自 \"internationalization\", 共 20 个字母）是让产品或服务更容易适应各种文化的最佳实践。</p>\n<blockquote>\n  <p><strong>国际化</strong>是指在设计和开发产品、应用或文档内容时，为不同文化、地区或语言的目标受众提供方便的本地化服务。（<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/W3C\">W3C <small>(en-US)</small></a> 定义）</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>在其他方面，i18n 仍然需要许多支持</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>字符集（通常使用 <a href=\"https://searchcio-midmarket.techtarget.com/definition/Unicode\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Unicode</a>）</li>\n  <li>计量单位（货币、°C/°F、km/miles 等）</li>\n  <li>时间和日期格式</li>\n  <li>键盘布局</li>\n  <li>文字书写顺序</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本知识","title":"基本知识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internationalization_and_localization\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">i18n</a> on Wikipedia</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术参考","title":"技术参考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/International/questions/qa-i18n.en#Internationalization\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">i18n on W3C</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gala-global.org/what-internationalization\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">i18n on gala-global.org</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"学习_i18n","title":"学习 i18n","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"http://www.i18nguy.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">i18n material on i18nguy.com</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"i18n（取自 \"internationalization\", 共 20 个字母）是让产品或服务更容易适应各种文化的最佳实践。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"I18N","loca